#

Balsamic Glazed Chicken Thighs

$12.5
520 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

ChickenGluten-FreeSavory

Description

Juicy chicken thighs enveloped in a rich balsamic glaze, perfect for a quick weeknight dinner.

Ingredients

  • Chicken Thighs: 4 pieces
  • Balsamic Vinegar: 1/2 cup
  • Honey: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Fresh Rosemary: 1 tablespoon, chopped
